    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众梁山兵",
        "卢俊义",
        "史文恭",
        "曾大虎",
        "林冲",
        "燕青"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爱习拳棒，论英雄，四海名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两膀千斤力无穷，药箭伤人掌握中。庄下儿郎似猛虎，要把梁山一扫空！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众庄丁自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，史文恭。曾拜周侗老师，习就全身武艺。前番劫了段景住宝马一匹，那段"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "景住去到梁山，搬弄是非。那晁盖听信他言，带领梁山人马攻打我庄，被某一"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "箭，射死晁天王。那梁山必不甘休，我命人前去扫探，未见到来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曾大虎、曾氏四虎同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曾大虎",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梁山拜庄事，报与师爷知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曾大虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见师爷。今有梁山，挂卢俊义为帅，前来拜庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭出乎意料，略加思索。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少时卢爷到此，看为师眼色行事。有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曾大虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。众梁山兵、燕青、林冲、卢俊义同上。史文恭出迎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，师弟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，师兄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我弟兄久违了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久违了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭、卢俊义同笑，卢俊义进门。史文恭向林冲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，师弟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林冲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭、林冲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久违了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭、林冲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭、林冲同笑。燕青与史文恭比粗，林冲拉燕青同进，众梁山兵暗藏兵刃同随入。史文恭注意观察，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭、林冲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已发觉对方来意，进内让卢俊义、林冲入座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知师兄、师弟驾到，未曾远迎，当面恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等来得鲁莽，师弟海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢哪，岂敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊师兄，为何军家打扮？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为师弟而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭故作不解。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为小弟何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只为你前番射死晁大哥，众家哥弟纷纷议论，忠义堂挂愚兄为帅，要报一箭之"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄！既是梁山要报一箭之仇，师兄你何言为弟而来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是啊，我与贤弟同堂学艺，特地前来相劝贤弟，归顺梁山，以解此围。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄此言差矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何差？"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想你我弟兄，曾拜周侗老师，习学全身武艺，指望扬名天下，报效国家。林师"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟，在万马军中曾为教头，被高俅所害，他万般无奈，投奔梁山。想师兄你，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "居住大名府，家财豪富，谁人不知，哪个不晓？怎么你也归顺那梁山贼寇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（燕青拂袖。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日又来顺说小弟归降，师兄此言，谨慎哪，谨慎！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭傲慢。卢俊义示意使林冲进言。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林冲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊二师兄，想梁山替天行道，你就该听大师兄相劝，归顺梁山，以解此围。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师弟！我与那梁山呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已成仇，难免得两下争斗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师弟！不听兄言，终须后悔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉——𠲔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金枪一举鬼神愁，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何惧那梁山贼寇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（燕青怒目相视，卢俊义止之。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅你一人，济得甚事！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺史文恭呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拚一个生死方休，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕他刀割人头！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭断然。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻言怒气冲牛斗，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你怎能罢休！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "史文恭！愚兄再三相劝，执意不听，真乃匹夫之辈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄，哪个是匹夫？"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是匹夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曾大虎、曾氏四虎、众庄丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们是匹夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众梁山兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们是匹夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭拦住。众庄丁、曾大虎、曾氏四虎自上场门同暗下。史文恭两望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄！我若不念同堂学艺，想你等进得我庄，休想出去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早知你庄厉害，敢把卢爷怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众庄丁、曾大虎、曾氏四虎各执兵器同暗上，众梁山兵同露出兵刃。史文恭两望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄！听你之言，要与小弟较量么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卢爷何惧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此小弟得罪了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众庄丁、曾大虎、曾氏四虎、众梁山兵、燕青、林冲同下。史文恭、卢俊义同脱外衣，对打快枪，接枪架"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子，双收下。林冲上，曾氏四虎同上，对打，曾氏四虎同下。曾大虎上，打林冲下。燕青上，打曾大虎下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾氏四虎同上，同与燕青对打，曾大虎上，打燕青下，众人同退下。燕青自下场门上，出庄逃走，自上场门"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下。曾大虎、曾氏四虎同追上。）"
